{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ffd76d0816","title":"关于歼灭大同之敌的意见","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0c4ad2ab49","index":0,"year":1946,"month":8,"day":30,"articleId":"ffd76d0816"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji22","name":"毛泽东全集第22卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji22.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji22":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"c3afd36490","type":"paragraph","text":"关于歼灭大同之敌的意见","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"ffd76d0816"},{"id":"a065b86c7f","type":"paragraph","text":"（1946年8月30日）张、罗，并告慧，费问","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"ffd76d0816"},{"id":"9fd59469f3","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）大同敌有固守顽抗与突围西富两种可能。（二）你们应加紧消灭城外据点，并布置力量于其分路出击时（例如最近两次城内政人分路出击），包围齐灭之（最近两次只击溃未轩灭），以促进城内敌人恐悦心理，准备攻城，夺取大同。（三）如大同敌全部突围西重，则不要拦阻，让其第至离城数十里时外灭之。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"ffd76d0816"},{"id":"e2f06306a2","type":"paragraph","text":"军委","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"ffd76d0816"},{"id":"992c0f1b6e","type":"paragraph","text":"未三十[1]这是毛泽东为中共中央军委起草的给大同前线指挥部司令员张宗逊和政治委员罗瑞卿的电报。[2]，指楚荣臻，当时任晋察翼军区司令员兼政治委员。贺，指贺","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"ffd76d0816"}],"page":{"id":"9050ea0921","publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"ffd76d0816","start":116,"end":116}}}},"__N_SSG":true}